<div class="cb-admin-session-grid">
    <div class="cb-admin-session-card is-warning">
        <div class="cb-admin-session-card-title">Idle timeout yaklaşımı</div>
        <div class="cb-admin-session-card-text">Kritik degisikliklerden once session boundary yeniden degerlendirilebilir; timeout durumunda yonlendirme tek auth shell'e gider.</div>
        <a asp-area="Admin" asp-controller="Admin" asp-action="SessionExpired" class="cb-admin-session-card-link">Session expired ekranını gör</a>
    </div>
    <div class="cb-admin-session-card is-info">
        <div class="cb-admin-session-card-title">Başka cihazda aktif oturum olabilir</div>
        <div class="cb-admin-session-card-text">Coklu cihaz veya lokasyon sinyalleri security event timeline'i ve auth karar zinciri ile birlikte ele alinir.</div>
        <a asp-area="Admin" asp-controller="Admin" asp-action="SecurityEvents" class="cb-admin-session-card-link">Security events</a>
    </div>
    <div class="cb-admin-session-card is-neutral">
        <div class="cb-admin-session-card-title">Security-sensitive action note</div>
        <div class="cb-admin-session-card-text">Execution gate, crisis ve policy write akislari ayri command envelope ve audit reason ile korunur.</div>
        <a asp-area="Admin" asp-controller="Admin" asp-action="Settings" class="cb-admin-session-card-link">Guarded settings</a>
    </div>
</div>
